            "title": "The Peruvian Long-­Snouted Bat, Platalina genovensium Thomas, 1928 (Phyllostomidae, Lonchophyllinae), in the Area of Influence of the PERU LNG Gas Pipeline: Population Status and Recommendations for Conservation",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Hugo T Zamora",
                    "lastName": "Meza"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
